### Contest API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@userToken = YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create Contest (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "Contest #1",
  "title": "Weekly Contest 1",
  "description": "First weekly programming contest with exciting challenges",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/contest-image.jpg",
  "startTime": "2026-01-25T10:00:00",
  "durationSeconds": 7200,
  "prizePool": "[{\"place\": \"1st\", \"prize\": \"$500\"}, {\"place\": \"2nd\", \"prize\": \"$300\"}, {\"place\": \"3rd\", \"prize\": \"$200\"}]",
  "problems": [
    {
      "problemId": 1,
      "symbol": "A",
      "points": 500,
      "orderIndex": 0
    },
    {
      "problemId": 2,
      "symbol": "B",
      "points": 1000,
      "orderIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "problemId": 3,
      "symbol": "C",
      "points": 1500,
      "orderIndex": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Get All Contests (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests

### 3. Get All Contests (Authenticated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4. Get Contest by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1

### 5. Get Contest by ID (Authenticated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6. Register for Contest
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1/register
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 7. Get Contest Problems
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1/problems

### 8. Get Contest Problems (Authenticated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1/problems
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 9. Submit Solution to Contest Problem
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contestId": 1,
  "problemId": 1,
  "code": "function twoSum(nums, target) {\n    const map = new Map();\n    for (let i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {\n        const complement = target - nums[i];\n        if (map.has(complement)) {\n            return [map.get(complement), i];\n        }\n        map.set(nums[i], i);\n    }\n    return [];\n}",
  "language": "javascript"
}

### 10. Get Contest Standings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1/standings

### 11. Finalize Contest (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/1/finalize
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
